{"tid":2357192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：警察學院爆發急性腸胃炎　38學員毋須入院情況穩定","createTime":"2021-01-07T09:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T09:33:33.000Z","uid":290404,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f04e8c025dc40c4b5e78681108291833d070aad7","tid":2357192,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>黃竹坑警察學院爆發急性腸胃炎個案，38名學員出現病徵，毋須入院，情況穩定。</strong><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心調查有關事件，個案涉及17名男學員及11名女學員，年齡介乎20至36歲，他們自星期二起陸續出現腹痛、嘔吐及腹瀉等病徵，全部人均已求醫。<br />\n<br />\n防護中心已派員到場視察，並對學院進行醫學監察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569178-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569178-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=1ae5ad20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569178-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8cd2ca31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569178-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"dd1522227299a0ef2f6ef3f8be4d096b24eee6e5","tid":2357192,"uid":368265,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"食咗屎？"},{"pid":"cb6f7aae6aa5229f2d5704c3efcc3375f0ff713b","tid":2357192,"uid":165136,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"抗疫期間為醫療系統增加壓力<br />\n添煩添亂"},{"pid":"9e06f261a887727cb08ec7e68cadcafe0e95c5dc","tid":2357192,"uid":80851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"凍撚水？"},{"pid":"899e5562dc5d3e4f18a6ed3dd9d6ab52b9a62b2b","tid":2357192,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e06f261a887727cb08ec7e68cadcafe0e95c5dc","tid":2357192,"uid":80851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score